  <answer><![CDATA[<p>Yes you can view your booking online and make a payment by heading to our ‘manage my booking’ page, you will need your booking reference, lead passenger surname and departure date to log in: <span><a href="https://my.inghams.co.uk/login">https://my.inghams.co.uk/login</a></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p>If you have booked through a travel agent please refer to them directly to pay for your holiday.</p>]]></answer>
